data.description: Lovingly cared for Home Sweet Home, Just Listed in Watsonville's 55+ Community of Pajaro Village.  This single level home sits on one of the larger lots in the neighborhood and is just waiting for its new owner.  The property has been well maintained and features two good size bedrooms and two full bathrooms with an attached two car garage.  There is abundant natural light throughout the house from the good sized windows and the sliding glass door in the living room cerates a nice indoor / outdoor flow to the back yard.  Relax in the covered patio area and take in the mature fruit trees and nicely landscaped and fully fenced back yard.  The front yard features drought tolerant low maintenance landscaping.  Residents have access to the community swimming pool, hot tub, gym, spa & exercise facility for those looking to stay active.  There is a also a neighborhood library and opportunities for community activities and the option of Boat & RV Parking.  This is a special community and these homes offer a nice alternative to mobile home parks.
